{
  "stem": "26792.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vaboulis is a man who has helped so many Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Chekists said, we are not going to punish him for-- for helping Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are going to punish him for what he has done during the Soviet occupation against us, against the Cheka.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was arrested on the 10th-- [INAUDIBLE] on the 1st of February, 1946.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not arrested, but detained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was arrested the first one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they followed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wanted to see who I meet, what people I associate with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took me for 10 days' detention in the cellars of the KGB, which was a horrible time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the 10th of February, which is the Red Army Day, they let me out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was so weakened and so frightened that I didn't know where to go home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't know the way to go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Absolutely exhausted, I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they followed me a long time, wanted to see what I'm doing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what [? they're ?] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so what happened next?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But how did you meet your-- did you meet your brother in the meantime, since you came back?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother came to Riga to see me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to the prosecutor, to the public prosecutor, [INAUDIBLE], because [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nanc ?] was already in prison then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in all seriousness, I said to the [INAUDIBLE], he is an innocent man, but he has saved my life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, as a Jewess, am coming to you [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to take me instead of him, because I am as innocent as he is.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'm ready to go to prison for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And please release him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Bohomof ?] was his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that all right?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
